title: Episode #104 - Mo Mandel & ME
description: Comedian Mo Mandel and I hang out in the Mancave and laugh not only about a show we did with 12 other comics called Reality Bites Back, but a prank I pulled on Kyle Cease that never came to fruition, Shcumers rise to the top, and how Donnell Rawling thought MO wasn't funny.
